title: Ideal Pet Products Fast Fit Patio Door for Pets
description: Designed To Fit ALUMINUM Sliding Patio Doors - Simplify your life with the 5 in. x 7 in. Small White Aluminum Perfect Pet Patio Door. Give your small furry friend access to shelter day and night and get them in out of the heat, rain and cold without any fuss or scratching at the door. Economical and dependable, the Perfect Pet Patio doors require no changes to your existing sliding patio door and can be installed or removed with ease. Keep your pet safe and happy with the Perfect Pet Door.
